<subSubSection pageId="24" pageNumber="23" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="24.[192,1440,198,383]" pageId="24" pageNumber="23">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[192,311,198,222]" pageId="24" pageNumber="23">Remark.</emphasis>
The genus 
<taxonomicName box="[459,624,198,222]" class="Insecta" family="Melolonthidae" genus="Paulosawaya" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="24" pageNumber="23" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[459,624,198,222]" italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="23">Paulosawaya</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was originally placed in the tribe 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Burmeister" authorityYear="1855" box="[1060,1222,198,222]" class="Insecta" family="Melolonthidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="24" pageNumber="23" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="tribe" tribe="Pachydemini">Pachydemini</taxonomicName>
by 
<bibRefCitation author="Martinez, A. &amp; M. A. V. D'Andretta" pageId="24" pageNumber="23" pagination="345 - 356" refId="ref18871" refString="Martinez, A., and M. A. V. D'Andretta. 1956. Dos generos e especies novos de Pachydemini do Equador (Col. Scarabaeoidea, Melolonthidae). Papeis Avulsos do Departamento de Zoologia 12 (17): 345 - 356." type="journal article" year="1956">Martínez and D’Andretta (1956)</bibRefCitation>
. Later it was transferred to the tribe 
<taxonomicName authority="(Martinez 1975)" baseAuthorityName="Martinez" baseAuthorityYear="1975" box="[857,1244,230,254]" class="Insecta" family="Melolonthidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="24" pageNumber="23" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="tribe" tribe="Macrodactylini">
Macrodactylini (
<bibRefCitation author="Martinez, A." box="[1055,1236,230,254]" pageId="24" pageNumber="23" pagination="227 - 251" refId="ref18836" refString="Martinez, A. 1975. Contribucion al conocimiento de los Pachydemini neotropicales (Col. Scarabaeidae, Melolonthinae). Entomologischen Arbeiten aus dem Museum G. Frey 26: 227 - 251." type="journal article" year="1975">Martínez 1975</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
, but was considered 
<emphasis box="[253,420,262,286]" italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="23">incertae sedis</emphasis>
by 
<bibRefCitation author="Katovich, K." box="[465,665,262,286]" pageId="24" pageNumber="23" pagination="1 - 78" refId="ref18612" refString="Katovich, K. 2008. A generic-level phylogenetic review of the Macrodactylini (Coleoptera: Scarabaeidae: Melolonthinae). Insecta Mundi 23: 1 - 78." type="journal article" year="2008">Katovich (2008)</bibRefCitation>
. When I examined 
<specimenCount box="[901,1083,262,287]" pageId="24" pageNumber="23" type="generic" typeStatus="paratypes">four paratypes</specimenCount>
of 
<taxonomicName box="[1120,1440,262,286]" class="Insecta" family="Melolonthidae" genus="Paulosawaya" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="24" pageNumber="23" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ornatissima">
<emphasis box="[1120,1440,262,286]" italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="23">Paulosawaya ornatissima</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from the HAHC, it was immediately obvious that this species belongs in the genus 
<taxonomicName box="[1202,1353,294,318]" class="Insecta" family="Melolonthidae" genus="Clavipalpus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="24" pageNumber="23" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1202,1353,294,318]" italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="23">Clavipalpus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. These specimens match the latest definition of the genus 
<taxonomicName box="[805,954,326,350]" class="Insecta" family="Melolonthidae" genus="Clavipalpus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="24" pageNumber="23" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[805,954,326,350]" italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="23">Clavipalpus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by 
<bibRefCitation author="Katovich, K." box="[995,1192,326,350]" pageId="24" pageNumber="23" pagination="1 - 78" refId="ref18612" refString="Katovich, K. 2008. A generic-level phylogenetic review of the Macrodactylini (Coleoptera: Scarabaeidae: Melolonthinae). Insecta Mundi 23: 1 - 78." type="journal article" year="2008">Katovich (2008)</bibRefCitation>
. The transfer is here made, placing the generic name 
<taxonomicName box="[581,744,358,382]" class="Insecta" family="Melolonthidae" genus="Paulosawaya" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="24" pageNumber="23" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[581,744,358,382]" italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="23">Paulosawaya</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in synonymy with 
<taxonomicName box="[972,1121,358,382]" class="Insecta" family="Melolonthidae" genus="Clavipalpus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="24" pageNumber="23" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[972,1121,358,382]" italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="23">Clavipalpus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
